   =20
      EthereumMax
   =20
 =20
I have to say, if you are a plaintiffs=E2=80=99 lawyer and you see=C2=A0Kim=
 Kardashian and Floyd Mayweather Jr. post unqualified endorsements of some =
nonsensical cryptocurrency on social media, you should really drop whatever=
 you=E2=80=99re doing and type up a lawsuit right away. How hard can it be?=
 How did this take so long?Kim Kardashian, Floyd Mayweather Jr. , and Paul =
Pierce are among a number of celebrities being sued for allegedly leading i=
nvestors into a cryptocurrency =E2=80=9Cpump and dump=E2=80=9D scam.The cel=
ebrities and other defendants are accused of making =E2=80=9Cfalse or misle=
ading statements to investors about EthereumMax through social media advert=
isements and other promotional activities,=E2=80=9D according to the class-=
action complaint filed last Friday in the U.S. District Court for the Centr=
al District of California. In addition to the three celebrities, defendants=
 include the co-founders of the company and others.The lawsuit alleges Ethe=
reumMax is a =E2=80=9Cspeculative digital token created by a mysterious gro=
up of cryptocurrency developers.=E2=80=9D It says the celebrities told thei=
r millions of social-media followers to buy the cryptocurrency, only to sel=
l when the price was inflated.=C2=A0Ryan Huegerich, a New York resident, fi=
led the complaint on behalf of himself and others who purchased EMAX tokens=
 between May 14, 2021, and June 27, 2021, and lost money, according to the =
filing.=C2=A0Here is the complaint. Here is the EthereumMax price chart. Et=
hereumMax launched at=C2=A0$0.00000005875 and got as high as=C2=A0$0.000000=
863 before falling back to a low of=C2=A0$0.000000017, these numbers are al=
l absurd but the point is that the high one has six zeroes and the low ones=
 have seven. I do think that there is a certain rough honesty and transpare=
ncy in these things in that, if you bought EthereumMax, your thought proces=
s has to have been =E2=80=9CI am going to buy this thing because Kim Kardas=
hian is Instagramming about it,=E2=80=9D which she was, so the price went u=
p, and then she stopped, so the price went down. Like, who was deceived abo=
ut what? What did you think EthereumMax was going to do, other than go up w=
hen Kim Kardashian posted about it and go down when she stopped?
