StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #00000=
0; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-botto=
m-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">occa=
sional inquiries</a> but really=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/26356098.267642/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyMS8w=
MS8xOS91cy9wb2xpdGljcy9yaWNoYXJkLWJ1cnItc3RvY2stdHJhZGVzLWludmVzdGlnYXRpb24=
