none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">no prosecutions</a>,[1] =
so I assume that for the most part congresspeople are not=C2=A0in fact insi=
der trading based on information they get in their jobs, though sometimes t=
he publicly available facts do look <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/26356098.267642/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlua=
