order-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: =
#ccc;">a leveraged VIX ETF</a>?)</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This strik=
es me as more or less sensible as a general matter, both because in general=
 I am a=C2=A0tiny bit suspicious of people with demanding non-financial job=
s who spend a lot of time trading portfolios of individual stocks, sorry,[4=
] and because in particular congresspeople make important decisions that mi=
ght be=C2=A0influenced<em>=C2=A0</em>by their stock=C2=A0<em>ownership</em>=
. If=C2=A0you go to Congress and ask it to approve a law that is good for A=
merica but bad for the profits of health-insurance companies or defense con=
tractors or oil companies or whatever, you do not want Congress to reject t=
he law because too many senators own concentrated positions in the affected=
 stocks. I don=E2=80=99t know how practical an improvement this is =E2=80=
=94=C2=A0the health-insurance companies and defense contractors and so fort=
h have other ways of getting senators on their side, and despite the name y=
ou might still know what you own in a =E2=80=9Cblind trust=E2=80=9D=C2=A0=
=E2=80=94=C2=A0but symbolically I suppose it is nice not to have too many c=
ongresspeople who appear to have a financial bias in favor of individual co=
mpanies.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But that is not a point about<em> =
trading</em>.=C2=A0The advantage=C2=A0of this bill is that it restricts=C2=
=A0<em>owning</em>=C2=A0single stocks,=C2=A0and that=C2=A0ownership is what=
 creates conflicts of interest.[5]</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">My quibb=
le here is that this bill is clearly being introduced in reaction to public=
 complaints about well-timed congressional trades, and I do not see at all =
how it could address those complaints? It seems somewhat unusual for Congre=
ss to get a lot of material nonpublic information about=C2=A0<em>individual=
 companies</em>. The well-timed congressional trading we have <a href=3D"ht=
tps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26356098.267642/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3c=
uYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjAtMDMtMjAvc2VuYXRvcnMtcGlja2=
